
brief:      "Halden — a single-origin coffee roastery in Bergen that roasts one lot at a time and names the farm on every bag. A cinematic scroll story about the journey from a hillside in Huila to the cup: the altitude, the hands that pick it, the roast curve, the pour. Mood: premium, calm, cinematic."
reasoning:  claude-sonnet-5   (questions · concept · plan · art-direction)
bulk:       claude-sonnet-5   (section codegen · self-critique; escalates to reasoning on repair)
design:     claude-haiku-4-5-20251001   (legacy/fallback tier)

[1m── PLAN ────────────────────────────────────────────────────[0m
  register floor (editorial-story): added missing beat(s) — turn
brand:  Halden
mood:   premium, calm
layout: origin-to-proof, editorial-brand-story
sections:
  0. masthead         [36mcinematic[0m/lg  A single quiet mark — Halden, and the line 'one lot at a time' — over a still, high-altitude image before any scroll happens.
  1. the-altitude     [36meditorial[0m/md  Establish where this lot grows: the farm named, the elevation stated as fact, why altitude slows the cherry and concentrates flavor.
  2. the-hands        [36mnarrative[0m/lg  The pickers: close, human, unglamorized. Selective picking of ripe cherry only, the labor the price reflects.
  3. the-crossing     [36mcinematic[0m/sm  Brief, almost wordless passage — the lot leaves the farm, travels to Bergen. A pause in the story, not a sales beat.
  4. the-roast-curve  [36masymmetric[0m/xl  Inside the Bergen roastery: this lot's actual roast curve, temperature and time, why the roaster chose a lighter, longer profile for this cherry.
  5. the-bag          [36mmodular[0m/md  The named bag: farm, lot, elevation, process, printed plainly — proof the story is not marketing, it is the label.
  6. the-pour         [36mcinematic[0m/xl  The cup: someone pouring, the color and steam, the end of the journey made physical and immediate.
  7. the-invitation   [36meditorial[0m/sm  Quiet close: where to find the current lot, and a single line inviting the visitor to Bergen or to order the bag.
  8. turn             [36meditorial[0m/md  give the piece its turn — the moment the argument changes gear

